                                             rdfs:range <https://onto.colossi.network/cdo#Cause> ;
                                             rdfs:comment "relates an Action to a Cause, indicating that an Action initiates a Cause." .


###  https://onto.colossi.network/cdo#interprets
<https://onto.colossi.network/cdo#interprets> rdf:type owl:ObjectProperty ;
                                              rdfs:domain <https://onto.colossi.network/cdo#Frame> ;
                                              rdfs:range <https://onto.colossi.network/cdo#Parameter> ;
                                              rdfs:comment "relates a Frame to a Parameter, indicating that a Frame interprets a Parameter." .


